archimate:DataObject.name: MetricMeasure
archimate:DataObject.documentation: A numerical value or text determined for a MetricDefMeasure that may be collected for a RootEntity; such as a connection or a dealer. A MetricMeasure might be part of a group of MetricMeasures realized at a specific moment (MetricMeasureGroup). For example; a value of .005 ms that represents average packet delay.
